trans-unit.source: Contains filter criteria for data extracted from a workflow instance in a <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Zawiera kryteria filtru dla danych wyodrębnionych z wystąpienia przepływu pracy w <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] A TrackingDataItemValue specifies the value of a piece of data extracted from a workflow.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]TrackingDataItemValue określa wartość elementu danych wyodrębniony z przepływu pracy.

trans-unit.source: It is used to constrain the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> in a query of the tracking data base used by a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: Pozwala ograniczyć zestaw <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>obiekty zwrócone przez <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>zapytanie bazy danych śledzenia używane przez <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>

trans-unit.source: You can add TrackingDataItemValue objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to specify that the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> be constrained to those possessing the specified set of extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Można dodać obiektów TrackingDataItemValue <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>Aby określić, że zestaw <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance>obiekty zwrócone przez <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName>można ograniczyć do te określony zbiór wyodrębnione dane.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> klasy.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Konstruktor domyślny inicjuje <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>na odwołanie o wartości null (`Nothing` w języku Visual Basic).</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: You must set all of these properties in order to configure the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.
trans-unit.target: Należy skonfigurować wszystkie te właściwości w celu skonfigurowania <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"></xref> class by using the specified qualified name of an activity, data field name, and <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""></xref> representation of a data value.
trans-unit.target: Inicjuje nowe wystąpienie klasy <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue"> </xref> klasy przy użyciu określonej nazwy kwalifikowanej działania, nazwy pola danych, i <xref uid="langword_csharp_string" name="string" href=""> </xref> reprezentacja wartości danych.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> properties are set according to the values specified by the equivalent parameters to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, I <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>Właściwości są ustawione zgodnie z wartościami określoną przez parametry równoważne do konstruktora.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>

trans-unit.source: FieldName corresponds to the name specified in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Nazwa pola odpowiada nazwie określonej w <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: FieldName can, therefore, be set to specify an activity field or property; a member of an activity field or property; or a single element of an activity field or property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: Nazwa pola w związku z tym można ustawić określone działanie pola lub właściwości; element członkowski działania pola lub właściwości; lub pojedynczy element działania pola lub właściwości (ani członkiem jednej), który implementuje <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>interfejsu.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable>
